                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1999-12-19</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Halka Chronic is one of my favorite geology authors. I think she has a way of explaining the difficult into layman's terms such that the general reader can unterstand what is going on. She has another series on this region as well. Use amazon's author search engine to find them, I think you will find them all very enjoyable.</span>
                  
              
